In Geneſ: 12. the Lord giues this commandement vnto Abraham;
               Gen. 12.1. 
               Get thee out of thine owne country, & from thy kinred, & from thy fathers houſe: So muſt all that will be the Sons of Abraham, get them out of their owne country, that is the world, & their kinred, that is the fleſh: and their fathers houſe, that is the houſe of the Diuell.

J wil not ſay (as perhaps J truelie might) that their fond and new-found opinions, are Sathans bals of wilde-fire vvherevvith they haue ſet on fire the Church of God,Valer. Ma
